{"type":"answer","id":177710,"parentType":"question","parentId":19274,"uid":32000,"contents":"估计你是刚接触LINUX吧，kali只是众多LINUX发行版中的一个特别版本。如果你LINUX都不熟悉的话，那Kali里的众多工具估计你也用不上来。<br>\n对于普通人，我觉得能把<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">编程随想</a>博客里面的有关【信息安全】的博文都看一遍并照着里面的思路做的话就足够了。<br>\nTA的博文里有好多扫盲及进阶文章，贴几篇：<br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/10/system-vm-0.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">扫盲操作系统虚拟机 (系列)</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/10/linux-newbie-guide.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">扫盲 Linux：新手如何搞定 Linux 操作系统</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/10/linux-distributions-guide.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">扫盲 Linux：如何选择发行版</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/06/privacy-protection-0.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">如何</a><a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/02/file-integrity-check.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">扫盲文件完整性校验——关于散列值和数字签名</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/06/privacy-protection-0.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">如何保护隐私（系列）</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2010/04/howto-cover-your-tracks-0.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">如何隐藏你的踪迹，避免跨省追捕（系列）</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2009/05/social-engineering-0-overview.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">扫盲“社会工程学”（系列）</a>","date":"2020-02-25","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":1}